		<RichText x="740" y="255" width="407" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幼兽侧身，突进咬合，造成<span color="#ffacff">85%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="421" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幼兽后空翻消失，传送至玩家身后使用爪子划击，成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="703" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幼兽张牙舞爪，在近处进行快速的左右两段划击攻击，均造成<span color="#ffacff">65%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">每受到一次直接<span color="#ffacff">雷元素</span><span>伤害，其怒气值就增长34%，值满时幼兽的外观发生明显变化，永久</span><span color="#dfbfff">进入嗜魔状态</span><span>，以</span><span color="#e599ff">雷抗减至-10%</span><span>为代价提升攻击频率。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
