		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">兽境类原魔造成的伤害都会附带「侵蚀」效果。兽境幼兽的效果为：每层每秒扣除玩家<span color="#ffcdbf">0.5%HP</span><span>的生命值，每层持续</span><span color="#ffcdbf">9.5s</span><span>，持续时间独立计算，可叠加。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
